regen.absent_element: tracking of all changes made to questionnaires and case records
regen.new_specification: Systems supporting OM should track and log all changes made to the questionnaires and case records to ensure traceability and accountability.

regen.absent_element: tracking all changes made to case investigations
regen.new_specification: The system should provide functionality to track all changes made to the case investigations, including configurations, revisions, publications, and status updates.

regen.absent_element: situation of version conflicts in reusable questionnaire libraries
regen.new_specification: The system shall detect and resolve version conflicts when multiple users attempt to modify the same reusable questionnaire library simultaneously.
